      <h2>Taylor Assessment</h2>
      <p class="sp2-section-intro">The tool that defined the post-redesign positioning.</p>
      <p>Taylor is the only psychometric in the world that measures <em>culture contribution</em> — how an individual's behavior pushes, pulls, or destabilizes the culture around them. Six archetypes, thirty behaviors, calibrated against Psynet's database.</p>
